.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
.claude/

## ────── OS ──────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## ────── Build artifacts / temp ──────
*.apk
*.aab
logo-source.png
# Debug screenshots dumped to the repo root during dev (e.g. _screen_debug.png).
*_debug.png
_screen_debug.png

## ────── Release signing (NEVER commit) ──────
# The Android upload keystore + its props file. Losing these blocks future
# Play Store updates (see app/src-tauri/keystore/README.md for setup).
**/keystore/*.jks
**/keystore/*.keystore
**/keystore/keystore.properties

## ────── Sentry ──────
# Crash reporting DSN lives in a local .env file, not in the repo.
.env
.env.local

## ────── Misc ──────
.sentryclirc

## ────── Graphify / backups / vestiges ──────
# Graphe de code local (~3.3MB, régénérable via `graphify update .`)
graphify-out/
# Backup avatars local d'Alex
_avatar_backup/
# Copie dist→assets vestigiale : le frontend servi est embarqué dans libapp_lib.so,
